Played as {{champion:111}} with {{champion:222}} {{champion:55}}{{champion:121}}{{champion:82}} 
versus {{champion:157}} {{champion:60}} {{champion:103}} {{champion:20}} {{champion:64}} 

Was mostly behind the enemy team, but things started to turn around about 8 minutes, with my team slightly leading for about 2 minutes 16 minutes in. 

The Katarina and Mordekaiser were questioning my choice of champion, but I was focused on peeling for my team, which would be why I ended up with 47 assists but the least number of points and not ascending at all. 
Ending up winning with an 8 point difference.
